      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite, regression testing, and configuration management consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Solver has documented regression test suite covering laminar and turbulent benchmark cases. Configuration management is partially implemented; no formal software quality plan exists meeting FDA guidance expectations for Class III device. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
