      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate convergence to analytical solutions for relevant flow physics including rotating machinery and non-Newtonian viscosity models.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed against Taylor-Couette flow and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Non-Newtonian Carreau-Yasuda model verification incomplete; no rotating frame verification cases available. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
