      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent method applied; GCI reported for all QOIs; discretization error below 5% for hemolysis index.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh study completed. GCI for hemolysis index is 9.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Near-wall resolution in impeller blade passages insufficient for fine mesh. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
