      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is the primary COU QOI and is used as primary validation metric. Velocity field serves as secondary QOI. Stress-based hemolysis model parameters validated in simplified geometry only, not full pump geometry. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
