      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation workflow with peer review; boundary condition setup verified against experimental conditions by independent reviewer.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of boundary condition setup or model configuration performed. Simulation workflow documented informally in lab notebook only. Flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model must be validated for rotating blood-contacting devices; model form uncertainty must be quantified.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on literature precedent; no model form uncertainty study comparing turbulence models performed for this geometry. Power-law hemolysis model used; Giersiepen-Wurzinger constants not re-calibrated for device-specific shear history. Model form uncertainty not quantified. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
