      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with uncertainty; sensitivity analysis performed to identify influential inputs; Monte Carlo UQ propagates input uncertainty to QOI.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed with 500 samples varying inlet flow rate and rotational speed. Hemolysis model constants (C, alpha, beta) treated as fixed; their uncertainty not propagated. Material properties uncertainty not included in UQ. Partial input uncertainty characterization. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
