      "acceptanceCriteria": "Computational model input parameters must be demonstrably equivalent to experimental conditions; any discrepancies quantified and their impact on QOI assessed.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profile in CFD assumed uniform; experimental inlet profile not measured. Pump surface roughness in CFD set to hydraulically smooth; actual surface finish not characterized. Equivalency of rotational speed between CFD and experiment verified only to ±0.5 RPM. Multiple unquantified parameter discrepancies. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
