    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepts the package under the Minimal profile with the understanding that the Monte Carlo UQ results provide sufficient probabilistic assurance for the intended regulatory submission context. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated; 7 assessed and 6 flagged as epistemic gaps requiring future work. The package is accepted conditionally pending resolution of model form and test sample gaps prior to final PMA submission.",
